## 3. `traning/` — Training Scripts

### [train_sd3_pix2pix.py](file:///home/nhan/Repo/UltraEdit/traning/train_sd3_pix2pix.py) (~1710 dòng) — Training cho Stable Diffusion 3

**Kiến trúc:**
- Model: `SD3Transformer2DModel` (DiT-based, không dùng UNet)
- Text Encoders: **3 encoders** — CLIP-L, CLIP-G, T5-XXL
- Pipeline: `StableDiffusion3InstructPix2PixPipeline`

**Các hàm chính:**

| Hàm | Chức năng |
|-----|----------|
| [load_text_encoders()](file:///home/nhan/Repo/UltraEdit/traning/train_sd3_pix2pix.py#64-75) | Load 3 text encoders |
| [tokenize_prompt()](file:///home/nhan/Repo/UltraEdit/traning/train_sd3_pix2pix.py#77-87) | Tokenize prompt |
| [_encode_prompt_with_t5()](file:///home/nhan/Repo/UltraEdit/traning/train_sd3_pix2pix.py#89-123) | Encode với T5 |
| [_encode_prompt_with_clip()](file:///home/nhan/Repo/UltraEdit/traning/train_sd3_pix2pix.py#125-158) | Encode với CLIP |
| [encode_prompt()](file:///home/nhan/Repo/UltraEdit/traning/train_sd3_pix2pix.py#160-219) | Kết hợp tất cả prompt embeddings |
| [parse_args()](file:///home/nhan/Repo/UltraEdit/traning/train_sdxl_pix2pix.py#145-506) | ~400 dòng argument parsing |
| [combine_rgb_and_mask_to_rgba()](file:///home/nhan/Repo/UltraEdit/traning/train_sd3_pix2pix.py#641-657) | Gộp RGB + mask thành RGBA |
| [convert_to_np()](file:///home/nhan/Repo/UltraEdit/traning/train_sd3_pix2pix.py#659-676) | Convert ảnh sang numpy |
| [main()](file:///home/nhan/Repo/UltraEdit/traning/train_sd3_pix2pix.py#697-1703) | Hàm training chính (~1000 dòng) |
| `main.preprocess_images()` | Tiền xử lý ảnh (resize, crop, normalize) |
| `main.preprocess_train()` | Chuẩn bị training samples |
| `main.collate_fn()` | Batch collation |
| `main.get_sigmas()` | Tính sigma cho flow matching |

**Training flow trong [main()](file:///home/nhan/Repo/UltraEdit/traning/train_sd3_pix2pix.py#697-1703):**
1. Load pretrained model + text encoders
2. Freeze text encoders, chỉ train transformer
3. Thêm extra input channels cho transformer (concatenate source image latents)
4. Setup optimizer (AdamW), scheduler (cosine), mixed precision (fp16)
5. Load dataset từ JSONL hoặc HuggingFace
6. Training loop: encode source/edited images → add noise → predict → compute loss
7. Validation mỗi N steps
8. Save checkpoints

**Flag `--do_mask`**: Khi bật, ảnh gốc được concatenate với mask (RGBA) thay vì chỉ RGB → cho phép region-based editing.

### [train_sdxl_pix2pix.py](file:///home/nhan/Repo/UltraEdit/traning/train_sdxl_pix2pix.py) (~1411 dòng) — Training cho SDXL

**Kiến trúc:**
- Model: `UNet2DConditionModel` (truyền thống)
- Text Encoders: **2 encoders** — CLIP-L, CLIP-G
- Pipeline: `StableDiffusionXLInstructPix2PixPipeline`

**Khác biệt so với SD3:**
- Dùng UNet thay vì Transformer (DiT)
- Chỉ 2 text encoders (không có T5)
- Hỗ trợ EMA (Exponential Moving Average)
- Hỗ trợ xformers memory efficient attention
- Gradient checkpointing

