| [SD3 Stage 2](file:///home/nhan/Repo/UltraEdit/scripts/run_sft_512_with_mask_sd3_stage2.sh) | SD3 Stage1 output | 2 (mixed) | 1M JSONL | 1e-5 | 2 | 8×4 |
| [SDXL Stage 1](file:///home/nhan/Repo/UltraEdit/scripts/run_sft_512_sdxl_stage1.sh) | SDXL-base-1.0 | 1 (free-form) | 4M JSONL | 5e-5 | 2 | 18×2 |
| [SDXL Stage 2](file:///home/nhan/Repo/UltraEdit/scripts/run_sft_512_sdxl_with_mask_stage2.sh) | SDXL Stage1 output | 2 (mixed) | 1M JSONL | 1e-5 | 2 | 18×2 |

**Hyperparameters chung**: 8 GPUs, fp16, cosine LR scheduler, conditioning dropout 5%, WandB logging.

